     <text:p text:style-name="P47"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#c3_De_la_democratie_en_Amerique_edition_1866_Vol_1_Chapitre_01.xhtml#cite_ref-3-n142" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">↑</text:span></text:a> La rivière Rouge.</text:p>
